Share this on WhatsAppSpread the loveThe Ogun state police command has arrested an Islamic cleric identified as Abdul Salami Yakub for allegedly defrauding some members of the public.
Following a petition by one of his victim, an Islamic cleric has been arrested for duping two sisters to the tune f N5.4 million in Ogun.
According to the state police, the commissioner of police received a petition from Rukayat Ibrahim ad her sister Oluwaseun against Abdulsalam Yakub who claimed to have a spiritual solution to her daughter’s problem.
A masquerade head, assorted charms and magic pots were recovered after a search was carried out in his house.
Ogun state police spokesperson, DSP Abimbola Oyeyemi advised Nigerians to be careful of whom they approach for help.
